articles.title: Teachers union chief Randi Weingarten says Israel's Netanyahu to blame for Hamas murdering hostages - New York Post
articles.description: American Federation of Teachers president Randi Weingarten appeared to insinuate that Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu bears some blame for the hostages that were brutally slain by Hamas.
